div.p:
00,001.

   

My Lord,

   

You have commanded me

   

To offer You

   

Seventy-Seven Thousand Service-Trees.

   

I shall obey Your absolute

   

Command.

   

00,002.

   

My heart

   

Is one of my homes,

   

But my heart’s only Home

   

Is God.
